@page "/docs"
@layout PublicLayout

<PageTitle>How Grow.IT Works - grow.IT</PageTitle>

<div class="contact-page footer-info-page">
    <section class="contact-hero">
        <span class="contact-kicker">How It Works</span>
        <h1>Save the information once. Reuse it everywhere.</h1>
        <p>Grow.IT is a working database, reporting tool, and portfolio builder for mission-led organizations preparing for grants, donors, loans, partnerships, and board review.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-grid-section">
        <div class="contact-grid">
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Build the organization profile</h2>
                <p>Save mission, organization details, team members, board information, documents, and operating structure so the basics are not scattered.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Track services and value</h2>
                <p>Add people served, programs, money sources, and service records so the platform can show what support was provided and what it cost.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="contact-card">
                <h2>Generate proof</h2>
                <p>Use ASC, reports, and exports to turn saved data into funding readiness evidence, impact summaries, and portfolio language.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-form-section">
        <article class="contact-form-card">
            <h2>The basic workflow</h2>
            <p><strong>Set up:</strong> complete organization details, invite the team, and add programs and money sources.</p>
            <p><strong>Track:</strong> save people, households, services provided, outcomes, documents, and follow-ups.</p>
            <p><strong>Use:</strong> generate reports, review ASC readiness, export data, and build stronger funding narratives from what is already saved.</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta">
        <div class="contact-cta-card">
            <h2>Need the in-app guide?</h2>
            <p>After signing in, open Documentation from the sidebar for the full workspace walkthrough.</p>
            <div class="contact-cta-actions">
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Start Workspace</a>
                <a href="/contact?demo=1&subject=Documentation%20Walkthrough" class="btn btn-outline">Request Walkthrough</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
